namespace Root

features
	SafetyElements {abstract}	
		optional
			Watchdog
			ErrorDebouncing
			ErrorHandling {abstract}	
				alternative
					FailSafeMode
					SoftResetOnError
			SelfCalibration {abstract}	
				optional
					FineOffSetCorrectionOverTemperature

				mandatory
					FineOffSetCorrectionOverGain

				optional
					SensitivityMismatchCorrection
					OrthogonalityCorrection
					AutomaticGainControl
			MARCHtestoninit
			BackgroundSelfTesting {abstract}	
				optional
					RAMtesting
					ADCclippingcheck
					ROMtesting

constraints
	BackgroundSelfTesting => ErrorHandling